show.description: In 'Sparta,' directed by Ulrich Seidl, follow the compelling story of Ewald, an Austrian man grappling with his identity as a non-offending paedophile. Set against the backdrop of Romania, Ewald finds solace teaching judo to boys. This thought-provoking drama delves deep into complex themes of personal struggle, societal taboos, and the search for understanding and redemption. Explore the poignant journey of a man navigating the boundaries of desire and morality in this insightful film.
